                "Description": "This category should be avoided as far as possible and should be used only for unspecified disorders in which there is a significant disability of learning that cannot be solely accounted for by mental retardation, visual acuity problems, or inadequate schooling.\n\nIncludes: knowledge acquisition disability NOS\nlearning disability NOS\nlearning disorder NOS"
